LeBron James<strong> on free agency</strong>: &quot;I have no idea at this point. I'll consider my family. Sitting down and considering everything, but my family is a huge part of what I'll do. I don't have an answer for your right now.&quot;<br />
<br />
LeBron James <strong>on his right hand injury</strong>: &quot;Self-inflicted. Post-game, after Game 1. Very emotional... the way we played, the calls that were made, I had emotions that the game was taken away from us.. Pretty much played the last three games with a broken hand.&quot;
